Line 9-inch round pan with plastic wrap; set aside. Beat cream cheese in large bowl with mixer until creamy. Gradually beat in milk. Add dry pudding mix; beat until blended. Stir in 2 cups COOL WHIP and all remaining ingredients except wafers. Spoon into pan. Top with wafers; press lightly into cream cheese mixture. Freeze 4 hours or until firm. Remove dessert 15 min. before serving. Unmold onto plate; discard plastic wrap. Serve with remaining COOL WHIP.